{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"9f98453d-aec0-4950-bc76-2bbf4b5fe0f8","title":"Rules","vault":{"fsPath":"repos/dendron-aws-vault","remote":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/cczhong11/my_note.git"},"name":"my_note"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[],"anchors":{"底层规律":{"type":"header","text":"底层规律","value":"底层规律","line":12,"column":0,"depth":1},"心理学":{"type":"header","text":"心理学","value":"心理学","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2},"倾向":{"type":"header","text":"倾向","value":"倾向","line":24,"column":0,"depth":3}},"fname":"life.rules","updated":1628141195329,"created":1623304331304,"parent":"1723e833-135e-4267-af98-9c0eb39b8260","children":["h6s7p8k77KvbLflNkzCTR","NgFU3sbOqrUKDdvNrGuEO","wNx5SzWlEQyWYtusyIURC","86HU4Ygh1FB6y6NTkKg6L","8KxQDXoAxvzHeX1TmfU7v","D6dBkgPQUSHeFjgQ4aDGz","dSczfOAxcaGopSJmpAuIe","pPufkfh2IvwlRS1oCmi0L","cUV7b2iIGY5DUhu4mfsHu"],"data":{},"contentHash":"75ac103c49335956a823af6ca14428b9","custom":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"rules\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#rules\"></a>Rules</h1>\n<p>知道做什么会出错，不要去做！</p>\n<h1 id=\"底层规律\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#底层规律\"></a>底层规律</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>人类\n<ul>\n<li>生存</li>\n<li>社交</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>人类的神经是受外界的影响而改变的，每个人的经历形成了每个人独特的世界观</p>\n<h2 id=\"心理学\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#心理学\"></a>心理学</h2>\n<p>认知吝啬者：我们总是寻求保存认知（心理）能量并<strong>将复杂事物简单化处理</strong>的方法。我们会<strong>利用经验法则</strong>去走捷径。我们会忽略一些信息以减少认知负担；我们会过度利用一些信息以避免去寻找更多的信息；或者我们只是按照最初的直觉，接受一个不够完美的选择，因为它已经足够好了。</p>\n<h3 id=\"倾向\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#倾向\"></a>倾向</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>可得性\n<ul>\n<li>峰终原理</li>\n<li>锚定效应</li>\n<li>简单联想</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>损失厌恶，害怕小概率事件\n<ul>\n<li>奖惩机制</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>寻求解释\n<ul>\n<li>避免怀疑，消除不确定性</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>快速分类</li>\n<li>性别的关注点不同\n<ul>\n<li>男性和其他男性竞争</li>\n<li>女性挑选男性，关注自己的孩子</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>自己\n<ul>\n<li>注重自己的利益</li>\n<li>高估自己</li>\n<li>自我欺骗</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>社会\n<ul>\n<li>寻求社交认同</li>\n<li>权威</li>\n<li>注重声誉</li>\n<li>互惠原理</li>\n<li>一致性原理</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/h6s7p8k77KvbLflNkzCTR\">Availability</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/NgFU3sbOqrUKDdvNrGuEO\">Bad</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/wNx5SzWlEQyWYtusyIURC\">Bias</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/86HU4Ygh1FB6y6NTkKg6L\">Consistence</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/8KxQDXoAxvzHeX1TmfU7v\">Impatience</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/D6dBkgPQUSHeFjgQ4aDGz\">Rewards</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/dSczfOAxcaGopSJmpAuIe\">Self</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/pPufkfh2IvwlRS1oCmi0L\">Social</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/cUV7b2iIGY5DUhu4mfsHu\">Vivid</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"0f1b48c7-3a25-4016-83a5-15864d7803ad","title":"Development","vault":{"fsPath":"repos/dendron-aws-vault","remote":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/cczhong11/my_note.git"},"name":"my_note"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[{"from":{"fname":"root","vaultName":"my_note"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":63},"end":{"line":8,"column":21,"offset":81},"indent":[]},"value":"development","alias":"开发"}],"anchors":{},"fname":"development","updated":1618381238346,"created":1612940782409,"parent":null,"children":["400115e9-30f7-4a13-9776-db059bc9cd42","xsX5v3ZsyJ0i6gf9","1bc3b45a-b6f4-4150-87d3-5bd5b6eb8c24","6cea4852-6e7c-4140-b476-85c07b48a642","a40ef849-d301-4d74-a778-e6d9469dfb5d","774ndd6du53l5k1awv074r0","09d9081f-3dff-453d-8488-7d2344cc8895","92917ea3-452e-48dc-875e-5cd0002041db","2e151826-cb22-4d89-8ce0-71dad7204ce8","baa39444-0da9-4c55-8df7-2a6f8f787fa4","62daf50d-a39e-463f-aabd-be53790281fd","3524d0a7-be73-45d6-847e-c970f5c1c760","eac0f243-05b3-4b95-bec3-848e33edbc40"],"data":{},"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"body":"\n","contentHash":"38357962f5a50c6fd7d318dfa66bea90"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"previewV2Enabled":false,"enablePr